Cell["\<\
Forward difference uses two evaluations: the current point and one step \
ahead. Truncation error is first order in h. Cheap but least accurate.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9858495177180023`*^9, 
  3.9858495188115616`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"cf79436d-4be5-7b4e-b22b-\
